            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              <BLOCKQUOTE class="ip-ubbcode-quote"><div class="ip-ubbcode-quote-title">quote:</div><div class="ip-ubbcode-quote-content">Originally posted by Fate Amenable to Change:<BR>So you can get a more accurate frequency but the position and time is now more inaccurate. </div></BLOCKQUOTE><BR><BR>Not only that, but what Pokrface said is also true.  In quantum physics, there is no such thing as a passive observer.  Observation occurs by way of interaction.  Interaction disturbs the state of what is observed.

              

              
              
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
